
    sh <(curl -sSf https://downloads.nordcdn.com/apps/linux/install.sh)

You should be added to the nordvpn group.
Log-out and back-in for new group to take effect.

<https://support.nordvpn.com/Connectivity/Linux/1325531132/Installing-and-using-NordVPN-on-Debian-Ubuntu-Raspberry-Pi-Elementary-OS-and-Linux-Mint.htm>

    nordvpn login

Copy link in "continue" and paste as <nordvpnlink> below.

    nordvpn login --callback "<nordvpnlink>"

<https://wiki.archlinux.org/title/NordVPN>
